data.description: Spacious and private  3 BR, 1BA cape cod  WITH BONUS ROOM UPSTAIRS on 5 ACRES in Saluda! – Enclosed front porch to relax  in the mornings – Picketed back yard - Beautifully  original hardwood floors throughout the home –  HVAC installed in Feb 2019 – Pellet stove in family room – Spacious kitchen with ample cabinet space , master bedroom downstairs. Also has a chicken coop in backyard and a storage shed ,  A little TLC and love and welcome to your forever home
